***

### How to add this to your GitHub:
1. Go to your GitHub repository where you uploaded `bot.py`, `Dockerfile`, and `requirements.txt`.
2. Click the **"Add file"** button -> **"Create new file"**.
3. Name the file **`README.md`**.
4. Paste the text above into the editor.
5. Click **"Commit changes"** at the bottom.

When people visit your GitHub page, this will be the beautiful front page they see!